author: Tasha Wibawa
title: Here are the countries with no reported cases of coronavirus
description: The coronavirus pandemic that first emerged in China has spread around the world at an alarming rate, but these 15 nations say they have not recorded any positive cases, despite some of them neighbouring hotspots.
